oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lenoir City Parade
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Street scene showing a childrens' Fourth of July parade. They are in costume and are carrying signs. One says "Patriotic through all the year" and the others name the months.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
